                "invention-title": [
                    "Low-cost combustion device capable of reducing carbon emission, low-cost gas fuel capable of reducing carbon emission and preparation method",
                    "一种低成本减少碳排放燃烧装置、低成本减少碳排放气体燃料及制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a low-cost combustion device capable of reducing carbon emission, a low-cost gas fuel capable of reducing carbon emission and a preparation method, the low-cost combustion device capable of reducing carbon emission comprises a mixing kettle, a gasifier, a hydrogen supply system, a natural gas source, a static mixer, a buffer tank, an air source and a combustor; the mixing kettle is of a specially designed multi-layer concentric cylinder structure; a bottom discharge port of the mixing kettle is communicated with a feed port of the gasifier through a pipeline; a discharge port of the gasifier is communicated with a feed port of the static mixer through a pipeline; the hydrogen supply system and the natural gas source are respectively communicated with a feeding hole of the static mixer through pipelines; a discharge port of the static mixer is communicated with a feed port of the buffer tank through a pipeline, and a discharge port of the buffer tank and the air source are respectively communicated with a feed port of the burner through pipelines. According to the invention, transverse and longitudinal multi-layer full stirring of materials is realized, uniformity and stability of material mixing are ensured, and continuous and stable preparation of gas fuel is realized; the heat value of the hydrogen-based mixed gas is increased, and the cost is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种低成本减少碳排放燃烧装置、低成本减少碳排放气体燃料及制备方法，一种低成本减少碳排放燃烧装置，包括混合釜、气化器、供氢系统、天然气源、静态混合器、缓冲罐、空气源和燃烧机；混合釜为特别设计的多层同心筒结构；混合釜底部出料口通过管路与气化器进料口连通，气化器出料口通过管路与静态混合器进料口连通；供氢系统和天然气源分别通过管路与静态混合器进料口连通；静态混合器出料口通过管路与缓冲罐进料口连通，缓冲罐出料口和空气源分别通过管路与燃烧机进料口连通。本发明实现了物料横向、纵向的多层次充分搅拌，确保了物料混合的均匀性和稳定性，实现了气体燃料连续、稳定的制备；提升了氢基混合气热值，降低了成本。"
                }
            ]
